comments: White (CHI) legally contests Banchero's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Isaac (ORL) jumps early for the rebound and while he is airborne, Drummond (CHI) places a hand on his body but the contact is marginal.
Although Caruso (CHI) makes contact with the ball, he reaches across Isaac's (ORL) arm and initiates illegal contact in order to get to the ball.
White (CHI) legally contests Anthony's (ORL) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Harris (ORL) initiates contact with Caruso's (CHI) lower body and affects his driving shot attempt.
Caruso (CHI) moves alongside Banchero's (ORL) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Wagner (ORL) is in a legal guarding position during DeRozan's (CHI) drive to the basket.  At the end of the drive, Wagner lowers his arm and the contact with DeRozan's arm is marginal.
Ingles (ORL) releases the throw-in within five seconds.
Vucevic (CHI) initiates more than marginal contact with Wagner's (ORL) arm during his shot attempt at the basket.
Caruso (CHI) initiates illegal contact to Isaac's (ORL) head in an attempt to get to the ball.
Harris (ORL) cleanly strips the ball and avoids making contact with LaVine's (CHI) arm during his upward shooting motion.
LaVine (CHI) commits a take foul on Harris (ORL).
